{
  "stem": "10.4",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What do you have in mind?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I said why don't we take some bushes or plant or grass and make it nicer so it will look like a hospital.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He said, how can we do it?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I said, you see, [?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Jup, ?] the gardener goes every week to the camp, to Raisko.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "This was a woman camp.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They planted there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They had vegetables and fruit for the SS men, for the SS.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I said, he goes every week there, and brings for the SS men things.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I could go with him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Well, you can go.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Fine, I'll let you go.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I told him, listen, I can go with you.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Let me know when.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The following week he comes back.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I can go.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I went up on truck with SS men, naturally, the guard, always him.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we came to this camp.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we come in.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And all of a sudden, first time in all four years, I see girls, women, you know?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They come running to me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I said, I want to talk to Genya Halbreich.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And here comes a girl, a beauty.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Tall, black hair.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That time, the women already grow short hair.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And she comes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I said I'm Sig Halbreich.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I'm Genya Halbreich.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she looks at me, and she said, come with me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And she takes me to the office.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There is an SS man, the man in charge, sitting there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And she said Mr.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So and So, this is my cousin.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He looks at me, he gets up from the chair, walks out in the front room, and lets us both alone for an hour.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I talked to her and I found out that she is married to a very distant cousin of mine.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I never knew him, even from Krakow.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we tell each other from where we are, what we're doing, where our parents are.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So shortly, and she said from now on, we'll keep in touch.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This gardener every time brought from her fresh vegetables, fruit for me, you know, lettuce.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Between this camp and this camp you had communication with main camp, Auschwitz, you know.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "From [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I found out there are people there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we had communications.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And she was a middle person, because he transported and brought with the letters.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We had to be very careful.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The letters, he was hiding in the flower pot, see?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Then, in the meantime, we put grass on there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So this was the way the resistance worked, you see?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I was the second time there.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
